ol.li:
Winder machine uses RFID barcode scanner. Configure this sensor using the following settings:

                     Name : rfid_scan


                     Protocol server : winder_mqtt_server


                     Source topic: rfid_scan


                     Protocol: rfid_scan


                     Data format: JSON


                     Data type: Custom


                     Schema:
                  {
    "type": "object",
    "properties": {
    "tagID": {
       "type": "string"
    },
    "readerName": {
       "type": "string"
    }
    }
}
